  "3226250": {
    "name": "Dustgrave: Prologue",
    "steam_appid": 3226250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘瘟疫肆虐，国内动乱四起，一度强大的达赫兰帝国走向了末路。当幸存的势力和入侵的国家争权夺势，冒险家和雇佣兵涉险进入这片充满机遇的土地，写下波澜壮阔的篇章。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建你的角色，踏上壮阔旅程，在真正的沙盒 RPG 体验中放飞自己，体验完全的自由。你的行为举止会影响世界及其人民。所有重要事件都会被记录下来。所有角色都会根据各自的道德准则和派系来评判当今事态。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你做出的选择不同，你帮过的人不同，游戏剧情也会有千差万别。你在《尘墓纪事》的每段冒险都独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《尘墓纪事：序章》包含《尘墓纪事：沙盒RPG》的头几个小时流程。正作将于今年晚些时候发布！从序章开始你的旅程，然后在正作中延续之前的进度，你将能够加入派系并无限制升级！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.poster.avif?t=1728575216\" width=800 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.webm?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.mp4?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>世界上发生的所有重大事件都会记录在案</strong>。角色会根据各自的性格或派系来评判你的行为是善是恶。你可以当一名强盗，饱受平民大众的鄙夷，但贩卖赃物也能是跻身进入当地犯罪集团的敲门砖！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/b8d8674e84e44dfcf8bfd22951e3049a.poster.avif?t=1728575216\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/b8d8674e84e44dfcf8bfd22951e3049a.webm?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/b8d8674e84e44dfcf8bfd22951e3049a.mp4?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>世界局势每时每刻都在演变</strong>。派系会相互争斗，掠夺和征服定居点。有些派系兴许会称霸一方，而有一些可能不复存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/cb2b92588428f3ba41331ef5f2aa6504.poster.avif?t=1728575216\" width=800 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/cb2b92588428f3ba41331ef5f2aa6504.webm?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/cb2b92588428f3ba41331ef5f2aa6504.mp4?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随心所欲，走出自己的路。</strong>你既可以加入天穹教派，当一名神职人员对抗异教徒，也可以偷走老百姓的苹果！前路无数条，随你怎么选：犯罪首脑、正义英雄、无情的雇佣兵或睿智的考古学家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/1f6b1f160a3e36c5a23cf16b5d5591fc.poster.avif?t=1728575216\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/1f6b1f160a3e36c5a23cf16b5d5591fc.webm?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/1f6b1f160a3e36c5a23cf16b5d5591fc.mp4?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在易于上手，难于精通的回合制战斗中碾压敌人！</strong>得益于独特的战斗系统，你可以尝试技能和物品组合。找到超强的组合，将不知天高地厚的敌人杀个落花流水吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/94515f22a03a6d9ad004cb8f783dd82f.poster.avif?t=1728575216\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/94515f22a03a6d9ad004cb8f783dd82f.webm?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/94515f22a03a6d9ad004cb8f783dd82f.mp4?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>利用潜行机制，做你想做的事。偷东西？可以！</strong>实施暗杀？没问题！监视人们睡觉？小事一桩！破窗闯入马克家并偷走他的秘密日记，却发现他是敌方定居点的间谍，从而触发任务？说得太具体了，但仍然行得通！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/8eb6c79996f0223d3d97ad29d4c22fa4.poster.avif?t=1728575216\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/8eb6c79996f0223d3d97ad29d4c22fa4.webm?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226250/extras/8eb6c79996f0223d3d97ad29d4c22fa4.mp4?t=1728575216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创建并自定义你的虚拟形象！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
